# Terraform - local working-dir artifacts generated by `terraform init`/
# `plan`/`apply`. Never commit state (contains resource attributes/secrets
# in plaintext) or the provider plugin cache. terraform-plan.yml's own
# plan_output.txt/tfplan are workflow-run-scoped and regenerated every run.
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
tfplan
plan_output.txt
crash.log
crash.*.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# Docs should not be pushed because it contains business strategy.
docs/SafePass
.claude